{"tid":2196273,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"楚撚記!!","createTime":"2020-09-09T18:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:10.000Z","uid":283071,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"38e6f6730efa9aa88f4bf2ff8d4a1ba97a6ca17b","tid":2196273,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"今晚去左食楚撚記<br />\n黃金粟米 <br />\n全晚最好食 好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原隻脆皮豬手 <br />\n凍既 唔夠脆 同唔夠鹹<br />\n椒鹽豆腐 <br />\n夠脆 夠嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑柏葉爆炒雞腎花<br />\n好鹹 本身唔打算叫白飯都叫左碗白飯<br />\n夾埋白飯食 味道岩岩好 柏葉好un  腎都有腥味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoWpAs3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoWpAs3.jpg&h=21fde539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JcfNyeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcfNyeL.jpg&h=54c26938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FepuMzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFepuMzM.jpg&h=e8770cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ri02m77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fri02m77.jpg&h=52b7afe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67e5396df9ec1bc6b3dc064d7f3d31df355cee65","tid":2196273,"uid":116087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"即係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04443e574bc4b7e850822c93c3d3d5beee1e19c6","tid":2196273,"uid":299794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"個粟米好似好好食"},{"pid":"1de30a8c209b3472d289b651252fa8fa0e45019b","tid":2196273,"uid":283071,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"67e5396df9ec1bc6b3dc064d7f3d31df355cee65","tid":2196273,"uid":116087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T18:25:51.000Z","msg